<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-46-0805 </DOCNO><TEXT>The development of information processing in nuclear research is discussedstarting with the early stages of electronic data processing up to thepresent. The information technologies applied over that period are consideredto be a part of the research technology. From the analysis of developmentsand current trends conclusions for science strategy and organizationare drawn concerning the further application of advanced informationtechnologies. 232 refs., 23 figs., and 25 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>